Erupt			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	DESC:A sand eel that has buried itself in the sand can quickly erupt from the ground and attack. This counts as a charge, except the sand eel can only move its speed (not twice its speed), and it gains a +2 on its attack roll (in addition to the normal bonuses and penalties for charging).	SOURCEPAGE:p.61
